{"tid":2029832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[外資撒資了］《路透》引述私人銀行家：富豪擬啟動Plan B 從香港撤資","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T16:24:51.000Z","uid":239336,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"eb88196da33efecc185b5061c35d89f95aad3ebf","tid":2029832,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"中國擬在港實行國家安全法，引發本港自由消失的擔憂，將會令到資金從香港撤離。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》引述一名歐洲私人銀行家指出：「我們的客人當中，有些對於去年發生的事件（逆權運動）有些慣性，認為事情總會有一天過去。但他們現時會以超速（step on the gas）將財富集中風險減少。」<br />\n該銀行家續說：「去年很多客人將撤資視為plan B，未有真正將資產移離本港，但現在我收到查詢這些豪客正啟動撤資計劃。」該銀行家所屬銀行管理2000億美元資產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200522/JU7KCXBJKWHJSU6DHJGQHCMTYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200522%2FJU7KCXBJKWHJSU6DHJGQHCMTYI%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BShjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=ac1367a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200522%2FJU7KCXBJKWHJSU6DHJGQHCMTYI%2F&h=4f0b505a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200522/JU7KCXBJKWHJSU6DHJGQHCMTYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571f3dd7573e1314077d2aafdd6b8dab3d90d526","tid":2029832,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd26fb2e25c784cd68d28ed0a0a66b405d6499ea","tid":2029832,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"